                    <i class="ri-shopping-cart-line mr-1"></i>Cart
                    <span id="cartCount" class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 bg-blue-500 text-white text-xs rounded-full w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center hidden">0</span>
